The repetition in the scene suggests a continuous flow, possibly reflecting the peaceful yet constant motion of water surrounding the raft. Unlike traditional detailed representations, this abstract artwork relies on color and form to tell a story or convey emotion, allowing viewers to derive their interpretations. Overall, this video captures a serene, minimalist essence through a compelling blend of basic shapes and a limited color palette.
